description: A lip colour that provides a splash of colour in a liquid-suede finish that lingers.
A long-wear, full-coverage liquid lipstick with a smooth, matte finish.
A long-lasting, full-coverage matte lipstick in liquid form.
An eight-hour wear, liquid-matte lipstick with a featherweight, comfortable formula that stays put and keeps color looking as fresh and flawless as the first swipe.
A highly-pigmented, liquid lipstick that's weightless on the lips and delivers long-lasting coverage.
A richly pigmented, silky-smooth, matte lip color that delivers 14 hours of continuous wear without smudging or dryness.
A plumping, lightweight liquid lipstick with an addictive whipped texture and soft matte finish.

It’s time to put your lipsticks on notice. Milani Amore Matte Lip Crème has arrived. This revolutionary, highly saturated liquid-to-matte formula dries to a soft, velvety finish for fuller-looking lips. Its double-sided, flexible plush applicator hugs the contours of lips, working to lock in bold, opaque color. Non-sticky, smooth and ready for all-night wear (up to 16 hours!), our Amore Matte Lip Crème is the ultimate transfer resistant kiss-me-matte.
High-definition color meets velvety matte with Revlon Ultra HD Matte Lipcolor. With a unique gel formula and a lightweight, moisturizing feel. For love that draws you in – in 8 shades.

NYX Soft Matte Lip Cream - "Amsterdam" - Pure Red- Neither lipstick nor lip gloss, this matte lip cream is a new kind of lip color that goes on silky smooth and sets to a matte finish. Soft Matte Lip Cream is surprisingly durable and unlike some matte lipstick formulas also moisturizing.

Give your lips a colorful makeover with the Revlon ColorStay Ultimate liquid lipstick. This lipstick is food proof and doesnt fade after meals. It's formulated with an ultra-conditioning topcoat, so you dont have to wear a separate topcoat. One-step application. Available in assorted shades.

Doll up your lips in plush and vibrant color! Our Liquid Suede Cream Lipstick glides on and sets into a striking matte finish. Velvety soft and waterproof, this long-lasting lippie creates a positively polished look with every swipe.

This is the long-lasting, transfer-proof color you’ve been searching for—no fading, no bleeding. The high-intensity color glides on with a moisturizing feel that lasts up to 24 hours. The result: bold lips without the dry-out and no need to re-apply
A highly pigmented cream used to customize colour for the lips.

This velvety smooth matte lip cream is a fluffy, mousse-like cream texture that feels soft and light on the lips while delivering bold, intense color with a high fashion matte finish. Ulta's Matte Lip Cream formula is so rich and creamy, lips are never dry.

Designed for styles ranging from modern minimalist to bold and dramatic, this high-definition, saturated formula starts as a traditional lipstick that's been liquefied and concentrated, resulting in a luxurious, moussey texture with a sophisticated, matte finish. It comes in an array of on-trend bold and everyday shades and features a Tarteist Paint Brush Wand with an ergonomically slanted, soft applicator so anyone can paint on precise pigment no matter your Tarteist skill level.
Go beyond gloss with Maybelline's LipStudio Color Jolt Intense Lip Paint - glides on to deliver a jolt of intense color.
Maybelline's Color Sensational Vivid Matte Liquid Lip Color has a creamy liquid base for a soft, cushiony feel.

L'Oréal's Infallible Pro-Matte Gloss is their first high-impact matte gloss that provides high-impact, velvet matte color without the dry-out. The unique Pro-Sculpt applicator allows you to create endless looks from a bold sculpted look to a nude ombre.

Rimmel's Provocalips 16 Hour Kiss Proof Lip Colour is an exclusive 2 step product that locks in vibrant color for 16 hours. It's so incredibly lightweight and flexible that it adapts to the movement of your lips. These seductively rich shades bring out that femme fatale in you! Wow color, incredible shine and zero trace!

LIPPY is a highly-pigmented, long wearing liquid lipstick designed to complement your favourite Butter London nail lacquers. Butter London's nourishing formula moisturizes and protects with shea butter, and vitamin E. Butter London does not add parabens or phthalates to any of its product formulas. It's colour without compromise.
A silky, long-lasting lip stain that keeps lips covered with bold color from AM to PM—no need to reapply or touch up throughout the day.
A lightweight, long-wearing liquified matte lipstick with a creamy and matte, color-rich formula.
A precise, fluid lip color with the potent effect of a lipstick.
